    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"DAA Taxa\"\n---\n\n\n\n\n# Differential abundance analysis\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\nAnalysis information:\n\n-   Method: maaslin3\n-   Taxonomic level: species, genus, family, phylum\n-   Group variable: diet\n-   Formula used: **~ diet * intervention + (1 | id)**\n-   Correction: **Benjamini-Hochberg FDR adjustment**\n-   Detection threshold: 0.1%\n-   Prevalence threshold: 10%\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\nFor a complete table of maaslin3 results, see [Species](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/species/all_results.tsv), [genus](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/genus/all_results.tsv), [phylum](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/phylum/all_results.tsv), [family](https://github.com/openresearchlabs/OGB_project/blob/main/output/daa/daa_taxa/family/all_results.tsv)\n\nThe following tables lists all associations that pass MaAsLin 3's significance threshold for joint or individual q-values, ordered by increasing individual q-value.\n\n\n\n\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-125699ea9a5d6a9c267f\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-125699ea9a5d6a9c267f\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of significant features for species - Total features analyzed: 215<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"GGB1266_SGB1699\",\"Waltera_intestinalis\",\"Dorea_longicatena\",\"Dorea_longicatena\",\"Ruminococcus_sp_BSD2780120874_150323_B10\",\"Dorea_longicatena\",\"Alistipes_communis\",\"Firmicutes_bacterium_AF16_15\",\"GGB2982_SGB3964\",\"Lachnospiraceae_bacterium\",\"Bacteroides_uniformis\",\"Firmicutes_bacterium_AF16_15\",\"Clostridium_sp_AF34_10BH\",\"Adlercreutzia_equolifaciens\",\"Agathobaculum_butyriciproducens\",\"Agathobaculum_butyriciproducens